thread.title: Modified Android O Boot Image for the Nexus 5X to Improve Performance and Enable aptX HD
thread.title_full: Modified Android O Boot Image for the Nexus 5X to Improve Performance and Enable aptX HD

author: Mishaal Rahman
title: Modified Android O Boot Image for the Nexus 5X to Improve Performance and Enable aptX HD
text: Looking to run Android O on your Nexus 5X as a daily driver? If so, check out this modified boot image by XDA Senior Member rachanta . It enables an Interactive governor profile made that is popular on our forums, enables aptX HD, and tweaks the thermal throttling configuration.
